# Sentiment-Analysis-on-Amazon-Reviews
Sentiment Analysis on Amazon Reviews using Machine Learning and NLP
## Features
* Cleans and preprocesses raw text data.
* Predicts sentiment using Machine Learning.
* Web interface built in app.py.

## Installation & Setup
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Pravalika1307/Sentiment-Analysis-on-Amazon-Reviews.git(https://github.com/Pravalika1307/Sentiment-Analysis-on-Amazon-Reviews.git)
    2. Install the required dependencies:
    ```bash
      pip install -r requirements.txt
   3.Run the application:
       Bash
python app.py

     
